Instructions to use (commands to run in linux given)

1) Install django 

sudo apt-get install python-django

2) Install haystack 

git clone https://github.com/toastdriven/django-haystack.git
cd django-haystack
sudo python ./setup.py install

3) Install whoosh

hg clone https://bitbucket.org/mchaput/whoosh
cd whoosh
sudo python ./setup.py install

4) Install mecab and python bindings

Information can be found at http://mecab.sourceforge.net/
sudo apt-get install mecab python-mecab

4) Download from github

git clone https://zodiac@github.com/zodiac/ankiResource.git
cd ankiResource

5) Create database

python ./manage.py syncdb

6) Run!

python ./manage.py runserver
